<!--
VOICING PLAN — 4155 Jesus Loves Me (Eb major)
Key: Eb (3 flats). Simple hymn with I/vi/V pattern. Refrain adds IV color.

Verse (mm.1-8): I "334" open, alternates with V. vi (Cm) in mm.3,7 for
  the "Jesus loves me" phrase. Ab=IV appears in m.8 as G#° in ABC.
Refrain (mm.9-16): Builds gradually. mm.9-12 lighter (2-note RH, 4-note LH).
  mm.13-14 full Eb5 in RH at climax. IV in m.15 pre-final IV→I Amen.

LH arpeggio in mm.2,6,11 for rhythmic variety between block chords.

TEXTURE ARC: Verse opens quietly, refrain escalates to Eb5 peak at m.14,
  resolves with IV→I final cadence.
-->
